posting_body: ['1 Month Free On A 14 Month Lease Term', 'Call our friendly staff at', 'show contact info', 'to schedule an appointment or fill out this form <URL>', 'Special Historic Building in the Heart of Hollywood', "Located at 1245 Vine St, in Hollywood's heart, The Villa Elaine is an impressive historic building.", 'Built in 1925, the brick facade, curved windows, and lush interior courtyard are striking and beautiful.', 'These carefully renovated apartments are historically reminiscent while affording the functionality and convenience of new construction.', "Each finish was selected to reflect the property's original charm vintage-style fixtures, navy blue shaker cabinets, open shelving, and subway tiles and beautiful new flooring throughout.", 'Pet Policy', 'Cats and Dogs Welcome.', 'Additional Fees and Deposit May Apply.', 'Call for Details and Restrictions.', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', 'Custom Kitchen Cabinets', 'Lots of Light', 'New Tiled Backsplash', 'Hand-crafted Built in Shelving', 'New Ceiling Fans', 'Marble-esque Counters', 'All New Bathrooms', 'New Designer Light Fixtures', 'All New Appliances', 'Spacious Floorplans', 'Crown Molding', 'Walk-in Closets', 'All New Flooring', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES', 'Courtyard', 'Elevator', 'Resident Lounge', 'On-Site Laundry', '1245 Vine Street Los Angeles, CA 90038', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
